{"tid":2033942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於平權 香港有三十一萬人持有BNO護照","createTime":"2020-05-25T03:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T08:45:00.000Z","uid":81211,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b42965d91dcb3a9fde5a9fd857018cc6ed0dd59e","tid":2033942,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2idf9T9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2idf9T9.jpg&h=248f1ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bkBtLsv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkBtLsv.jpg&h=64031296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200227201115/https://www.whatdotheyknow.com/request/634155/response/1523562/attach/2/FOICR%2057241%20Luke%20Lo%20final%20response.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20200227201115%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatdotheyknow.com%2Frequest%2F634155%2Fresponse%2F1523562%2Fattach%2F2%2FFOICR%252057241%2520Luke%2520Lo%2520final%2520response.pdf&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMhdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=de4e8c9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20200227201115/https://www.whatdotheyknow.com/request/634155/response/1523562/attach/2/FOICR%2057241%20Luke%20Lo%20final%20response.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nBNO既CODE係GBN  而跟據HM PASSPORT資料 截至2019年 有31萬香港人仍然續領BNO<br />\n<br />\n個人見解啦 英國政府自從脫歐之後 的確係需要引入新的投資者同高技術人士 依家吹風平權 我覺得似係英國政府想渣乾埋香港最後果代的高知識份子同富豪去英國<br />\n<br />\n而大規模平權係邏輯上係絕無可能 <br />\n因為大規模平權 代表英國突然要接納起碼31萬人 仲未計埋佢地既屋企人 即係起碼係60萬 根本無可能任何一個政府會肯突然接納六十萬人口 依班人本身對英國有咩貢獻同利益?<br />\n仲未計未領續但持有BNO既人士起碼係三百萬 咁其餘果270萬人點處理?<br />\n<br />\n加上以我認知的香港人 好大機會都係拿完本BC 一世都唔會去英國 最多去睇埸波 跟住就留番係香港做野 定居<br />\n果本BC只係當係後路<br />\n<br />\n所以就算平權 英國政府最多都只係會俾持有一定年數的BNO持有者 例如五年 可以獨得英國暫時居留權 俾你去搵工 你需要係一定時間內搵到工 仲要KEEP住兩三年 你既人工係高於某一個界線 先可以轉番BC<br />\n但係英國基本上係搵唔到野做..........<br />\n<br />\n所以最好既做法係 李嘉誠帶頭係英國大規模投資一個城市 成堆香港人去搵工 慢慢聚集 咁先有機會.........."},{"pid":"33c6a1ec64e78adac90b8d2915b54f71cd18973b","tid":2033942,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我推!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"11fdc0b729eb1caacfd5a12a91a574e7f96ef30b","tid":2033942,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdc9f147cd45c9ad7e2bd82a1a8cb67501b21eb","tid":2033942,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:19:48.000Z","msg":"無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50dd027338188496ca8eed4fab7eebe6b67a192","tid":2033942,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bb164f7cf2b4269d683144e9ef6d24601df537","tid":2033942,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b42965d91dcb3a9fde5a9fd857018cc6ed0dd59e","tid":2033942,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2idf9T9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k